    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      494.05,
      526.35,
      507.67
    ],
    "text": "premises. The Defendant, in his evidence-in-chief, admitted that he had served under the",
